mp; dentists, shops, libraries, banks, post-offices, bus services etc </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">etc</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">).</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">  Meanwhile, </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">crofting</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> lands are increasingly abandoned and unproductive as their tenants age.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">2.  The land-ownership pattern is sustained and rei</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">nforced by subsidy and taxation arrangements in </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">anumber</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold"> of ways:</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">-</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Subsidy and tax advantages inflate land values, which limits new entrants,</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">-</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">The use of land as an investment vehicle rewards speculation and inhibits innovation</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">-</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Subsidy and tax advantages ensure the price of land is divorced from its productive value,  which rewards inertia and inhibits sustainable development.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">3.  A Land Agency should</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> function to</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> enforce and proactively enable Land Reform</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> with a view to increasi</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">ng productivity, biodiversity, community buy-outs, community owned energy projects and liberating abandoned croft lands, assisting planning permissions for new builds on croft lands, creating new croft and woodland crofts as well as helping newcomers throu</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">gh the process of finding and purchasing land and self-build planning.   </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:i